    <title>hexo升级</title>
    <link href="/blog/2021/02/26/hexo%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/"/>
    <url>/blog/2021/02/26/hexo%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="hexo升级"><a href="#hexo升级" class="headerlink" title="hexo升级"></a>hexo升级</h4><ul><li><p><a href="https://tommy.net.cn/2020/08/08/upgrade-hexo-to-v5-0-0/">参考链接</a></p></li><li><p>好久没看hexo了，今天看了一下发现hexo和next主题都有大更新，索性全部更新到新版本</p></li></ul><img src="/hexo升级/image-20210226001944746.png" alt="image-20210226001944746" style="zoom:70%;" /><ul><li>查看版本信息，很多警告和报错，<code>npm update</code>更新后只更新了小版本号，依旧报错，上官网查看得知已经更新到了5.4.0，搜索更新方法，发现可以用ncu直接更新</li></ul><img src="/hexo升级hexo升级/image-20210226002043492.png" alt="image-20210226002043492" style="zoom:70%;" /><p><img src="/blog/image/hexo%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/image-20210226002813721-1614279677351.png" alt="image-20210226002813721"></p><img src="/blog/2021/02/26/hexo%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/image-20210226002813721-1614279677351.png" class="" title="This is an example image"><ul><li>安装ncu，检查更新，修改package.json，更新</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install npm-check-updates -g<br>ncu<br>ncu -u<br>npm install --save<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/blog/image/hexo%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/image-20210226002908644-1614279677351.png" alt="image-20210226002908644"></p><ul><li>更新成功</li></ul><p><img src="/blog/image/hexo%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/image-20210226003013704-1614279677351.png" alt="image-20210226003013704"></p><ul><li>启动服务，有一些警告，但是能正常使用</li></ul><p><img src="/blog/image/hexo%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/image-20210226003204665-1614279677351.png" alt="image-20210226003204665"></p><p><img src="/blog/image/hexo%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/image-20210226003131720-1614279677351.png" alt="image-20210226003131720"></p><ul><li>修改配置文件，把”use_date_for_updated”改为”updated_option”，再运行，报错消失</li></ul><p><img src="/blog/image/hexo%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/image-20210226004446423-1614279677351.png" alt="image-20210226004446423"></p><ul><li><code>hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy</code>一键部署，成功</li></ul><p>![image-20210226004534555](image/hexo升级/hexo升级</p><ul><li><p><a href="https://tommy.net.cn/2020/08/08/upgrade-hexo-to-v5-0-0/">参考链接</a></p></li><li><p>好久没看hexo了，今天看了一下发现hexo和next主题都有大更新，索性全部更新到新版本</p></li></ul><img src="/hexo升级hexo升级/image-20210226001944746.png" alt="image-20210226001944746" style="zoom:70%;" /><ul><li>查看版本信息，很多警告和报错，<code>npm update</code>更新后只更新了小版本号，依旧报错，上官网查看得知已经更新到了5.4.0，搜索更新方法，发现可以用ncu直接更新</li></ul><img src="/hexo升级hexo升级/image-20210226002043492.png" alt="image-20210226002043492" style="zoom:70%;" /><p><img src="/blog/image/hexo%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/image-20210226002813721-1614279710331.png" alt="image-20210226002813721"></p><ul><li>安装ncu，检查更新，修改package.json，更新</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install npm-check-updates -g<br>ncu<br>ncu -u<br>npm install --save<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/blog/image/hexo%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/image-20210226002908644-1614279710331.png" alt="image-20210226002908644"></p><ul><li>更新成功</li></ul><p><img src="/blog/image/hexo%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/image-20210226003013704-1614279710332.png" alt="image-20210226003013704"></p><ul><li>启动服务，有一些警告，但是能正常使用</li></ul><p><img src="/blog/image/hexo%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/image-20210226003204665-1614279710332.png" alt="image-20210226003204665"></p><p><img src="/blog/image/hexo%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/image-20210226003131720-1614279710333.png" alt="image-20210226003131720"></p><ul><li>修改配置文件，把”use_date_for_updated”改为”updated_option”，再运行，报错消失</li></ul><p><img src="/blog/image/hexo%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/image-20210226004446423-1614279710333.png" alt="image-20210226004446423"></p><ul><li><code>hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy</code>一键部署，成功</li></ul><p><img src="/blog/image/hexo%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7/image-20210226004534555.png" alt="image-20210226004534555"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
