  <entry>
    <title>blog搭建</title>
    <link href="/blog/2020/04/23/blog%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/"/>
    <url>/blog/2020/04/23/blog%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="nvm-nodejs-npm安装"><a href="#nvm-nodejs-npm安装" class="headerlink" title="nvm nodejs npm安装"></a>nvm nodejs npm安装</h3><p><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/hjson/p/10276532.html">参考链接</a></p><h4 id="一、-nvm的安装配置"><a href="#一、-nvm的安装配置" class="headerlink" title="一、 nvm的安装配置"></a>一、 nvm的安装配置</h4><ol><li><p>先下载<a href="https://github.com/coreybutler/nvm-windows/releases">nvm安装包</a>，推荐nvm-setup.zip，不需要配置环境变量，安装即可使用</p></li><li><p>安装好后执行nvm</p><p><img src="/blog/blog_%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/image-20200423152034153.png" alt="image-20200423152034153"></p></li><li><p>修改nvm默认源为淘宝源，地址一般在C:\Users\Test\AppData\Roaming\nvm\settings.txt</p><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs json">root: C:\myfile\nvm<br>path: C:\myfile\nodejs<br>arch: 64<br>proxy: <br>originalpath: .<br>originalversion: <br>node_mirror: https://npm.taobao.org/mirrors/node/<br>npm_mirror: https://npm.taobao.org/mirrors/npm/<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h4 id="二、安装node"><a href="#二、安装node" class="headerlink" title="二、安装node"></a>二、安装node</h4><ol><li><p>nvm安装nodejs</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">nvm  install version <br><span class="hljs-comment">#version就是要安装的nodejs版本，官网可以查询到。</span><br>     <br>nvm install v11<span class="hljs-number">.6</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><br>nvm install <span class="hljs-number">11.6</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#我安装了最新版</span><br>nvm install latest<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>查看版本</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">nvm <span class="hljs-built_in">list</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>切换nodejs</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">nvm  use  version <br><span class="hljs-comment">#例如</span><br>nvm use <span class="hljs-number">14.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>查看是否切换成功</p><figure class="highlight crmsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs crmsh"><span class="hljs-keyword">node</span> <span class="hljs-title">-v</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="三、配置nmp"><a href="#三、配置nmp" class="headerlink" title="三、配置nmp"></a>三、配置nmp</h3><ol><li><p>安装cnpm</p><figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs awk">npm install cnpm -g --registry=https:<span class="hljs-regexp">//</span>registry.npm.taobao.org<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>设置npm源</p><figure class="highlight arduino"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs arduino">npm <span class="hljs-built_in">config</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">set</span> registry https:<span class="hljs-comment">//registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>安装nrm(npm源管理工具)</p><figure class="highlight coffeescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs coffeescript"><span class="hljs-built_in">npm</span> i nrm -g<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h4 id="四、安装hexo"><a href="#四、安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="四、安装hexo"></a>四、安装hexo</h4><ol><li><p>先创建一个blog的文件夹</p></li><li><p>切换到这个文件夹，安装hexo</p><figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cmake">npm <span class="hljs-keyword">install</span> hexo -g<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>输入hexo -v查看是否安装成功</p></li><li><p>输入hexo init，初始化文件夹(这一步时间比较长)</p></li><li><p>输入npm install，安装相应组件</p></li><li><p>创建静态文件并且开启服务器，打开<a href="http://localhost:4000/%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E5%8F%AF%E7%9C%8B%E5%88%B0%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C">http://localhost:4000/，即可看到效果</a></p><figure class="highlight 1c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs 1c">hexo g<span class="hljs-meta">&amp;&amp;hexo s</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/blog/blog_%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/image-20200423161849011.png" alt="image-20200423161849011"></p></li></ol>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
